data.description: This Cumberland Terrace home boasts several improvements and features that make it an attractive option to make it your new home.  With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, this home offers ample space. Hardwood stairs, main level and second level. The kitchen is equipped with granite countertops and new LG stainless steel appliances (2021), including a bay window with nook for a cozy breakfast experience or entertain in the spacious dining room.   The large living room features a fireplace with gas logs and hardwood floors, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Additionally, the first floor offers a spacious family room and office, providing flexibility for various needs along with the convenience of a main floor half bath.   The stairs to the second floor lead to the left and right wings of the home. Right to the master suite, complete with a private bath and plenty of closet space. To the left offers 3 bedrooms and a full bath.    Outside, you will find a large fenced-in yard, perfect for outdoor activities, as well as a patio for relaxation. The property also includes a 2.5 detached garage with a side driveway, offering convenient parking options. Professional pet-friendly lawn service completed: including weed removal, aeration, and fertilization. Notable upgrades include an upgraded 200-amp electrical service, ensuring efficient power distribution throughout the home. The house is completely wired with cat 6 internet cable, providing high-speed connectivity. The LG washer and dryer (2021), as well as Lennox A/C and furnace, (2020) air cleaner, and water heater (2021) contribute to enhanced comfort and convenience.    Located in a desirable location, this home allows for easy access to nearby shopping amenities. Additionally, it is conveniently situated just a 2-block walk to the Metra, providing a hassle-free commute to downtown Chicago. Overall, this property offers a combination of modern upgrades and convenient features that make it an appealing choice for potential buyers. Located just blocks from Mariano's, parks, swimming pool, YMCA, schools and much more.
